      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，从左到右布局。那分支结构怎么设计？是一个main分支加一个特性分支吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，先让main分支有一个初始commit，然后从main切出一个叫newbranch的分支，在这个分支上再做一次提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit",
        "branch newbranch",
        "checkout newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把main的初始commit和newbranch的创建加上。切到newbranch后又做了一次commit，这部分完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch newbranch",
        "checkout newbranch",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来切回main分支，在main上再做一个commit，模拟主分支也在推进，最后把newbranch合并进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "commit",
        "merge newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下流程：切回main → main上新增commit → 执行merge把newbranch合进来。这样合并后会有两条线汇入main的效果，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
